K = 25
i = 0

    if s[i] != 0 and 26-s[i] <= K:
        K -= 26-s[i]
        s[i] = 0
    else:
        i += 1
s[-1] = (s[-1]+K)%26 
print(*[chr(x+97) for x in s], sep = '')
